Price increases. 



(a) Should the tour operator increase a participant's tour price by more than 10 percent (aggregate of all increases
to that participant), that participant shall have the option of canceling his or her participation in the tour and
receiving a full refund within 14 days after the cancellation.

(b) The tour operator shall not increase the tour price to any participant less than 5 days before departure.

